headline: If I Could Only Buy and Hold a Single Stock, This Would Be It.
summary: If I had to pick one high-yield stock today that would be worth buying and holding over the long term, it would be Realty Income.  Realty Income isn't exciting in the least, which is exactly why dividend investors like me love it.  The reason is partly because of its well-above-market 5.6% dividend yield, but there's much more to like beyond that simple fact.
